data.description: Discover this charming home in the highly sought after community of Blue Horizons, boasting a large and unique pie-shaped lot, RV gate, and 2-car garage. Experience a welcoming open floor plan with stylish wood-look tile flooring, formal dining area, neutral palette, and plenty of natural light. The spacious kitchen is equipped with built-in appliances, walk-in pantry, extensive cabinet and counter space, recessed lighting, chic backsplash, and an island with a breakfast bar. The main bedroom suite features a large shower, double sinks, and walk-in closet, while an additional bedroom offers a private bath, perfect for guests. The expansive backyard offers a blank canvas for your landscaping dreams. A must-see home that promises not to disappoint!
